00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:46,180
I forgot to bring my notes.

285
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:47,700
I need to go now.

286
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:54,130
Lung, I'm sure you can imagine
that without you,

287
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:55,100
how chaotic it is outside,

288
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:56,530
right?

289
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,820
There is no need to involve
all of your people.

290
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:07,610
Have a cup of coffee.

291
00:13:07,820 --> 00:13:08,300
Lung.

292
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:11,850
Allow me some time.

293
00:13:13,220 --> 00:13:14,460
If it's necessary,

294
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,100
how about I give you two days

295
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:17,010
to meet your son out there?

296
00:13:19,620 --> 00:13:21,460
Let your people go home and rest.

297
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:23,010
There is no need to make it serious.

298
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:27,490
Nothing is settled yet.

299
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:29,860
It's a waste.

300
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:34,250
Here.

301
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:42,780
Mr. Wu.

302
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:43,820
Any instructions from our superior?

303
00:13:43,820 --> 00:13:45,300
Release all the people

304
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:46,650
you arrested yesterday,

305
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:47,850
whether they are subordinate
to Chi Cheung-wing

306
00:13:48,180 --> 00:13:49,010
or Hon Fui-lung.

307
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:50,130
What?

308
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:52,850
We arrested three cars of people.

309
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,300
They hurt people
and caused criminal damage.

310
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:56,250
And we also smashed several
newly-found drug trafficking spots.

311
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,420
And now you want me to release them?

312
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:00,130
Have you ever seen me drinking coffee?

313
00:14:00,620 --> 00:14:02,130
Mr. Wu, don't beat around the bush.

314
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:05,010
It's decided by those who drink coffee.

315
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:06,770
They say harmony is important,

316
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:08,300
and they don't want further troubles.

317
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:40,890
Sorry, Mr. Sek.

318
00:15:41,740 --> 00:15:43,500
The coffee
at our Eastern District Police Station

319
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:44,730
isn't as good as
the headquarters' coffee.

320
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:48,530
You had such a good chat with Mr. Tat.

321
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,340
So what brings you here?

322
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,730
If Hon Fui-lung's son matters much,

323
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:55,820
what about the man he killed?

324
00:15:57,150 --> 00:15:59,130
You actually sympathized with him
and made a deal with him.

325
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:02,130
If so,

326
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:04,300
Hon Gong deserves it even more.

327
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:05,460
Will you let go

328
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,700
the murderer who hit him?

329
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,890
I know you're angry,

330
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,300
but we made a deal

331
00:16:18,270 --> 00:16:21,250
not to let the business
affect our feelingsï¼Œ

332
00:16:21,270 --> 00:16:22,010
right?

333
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:26,250
But to put it this way,

334
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,940
if your Regional Crime Unit

335
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:31,130
needs help from our Intelligence Bureau,

336
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:34,060
I don't mind

337
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,180
helping you

338
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:37,370
out of my personal feelings.

339
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:41,580
So I would like to ask you,

340
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:44,180
is it a clear distinction
between public and private

341
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:46,300
or the opposite?

342
00:16:48,390 --> 00:16:49,370
Let me put it this way.

343
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:50,530
It means

344
00:16:50,670 --> 00:16:52,610
I'll help you, Ms. Tong,
as long as you need.

345
00:17:17,590 --> 00:17:18,330
See you in the usual spot.

346
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:28,020
[Hokong Judiciary]

347
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:28,580
Mr. Chun.

348
00:17:28,780 --> 00:17:29,900
The court session starts
in half an hour.

349
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:31,260
And also,

350
00:17:31,270 --> 00:17:31,860
I wanted to tell you...

351
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,420
Ms. Sum is here.

352
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:35,180
I've retired,

353
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:36,570
and I'm no longer a judge.

354
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:38,180
I'm sitting here

355
00:17:38,180 --> 00:17:39,490
as Mr. Chun's mother-in-law.

356
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,900
Why did you come

357
00:17:40,900 --> 00:17:41,980
without telling me in advance?

358
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:45,010
Do you mean I shouldn't?

359
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,250
Should I come back tomorrow?

360
00:17:47,860 --> 00:17:48,460
It's okay.

361
00:17:49,260 --> 00:17:50,460
Then I'll leave now.

362
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:52,900
Sit.

363
00:17:53,220 --> 00:17:53,770
What brings you here?

364
00:17:55,700 --> 00:17:56,730
Why didn't you tell me

365
00:17:57,180 --> 00:17:58,330
that the car was stolen?

366
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:00,860
The car was once stolen,

367
00:18:01,070 --> 00:18:02,140
and now it's back.

368
00:18:02,590 --> 00:18:03,700
I didn't want you to worry.

369
00:18:04,300 --> 00:18:05,700
The car was registered in my name.

370
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:08,090
But I didn't even know it
until the Transport Department

371
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:08,980
notified me.

372
00:18:09,780 --> 00:18:10,290
Sorry.

373
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:11,660
I don't want to always be the last

374
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:13,010
to know about everything.

375
00:18:15,060 --> 00:18:15,980
Don't forget

376
00:18:16,180 --> 00:18:17,050
that you still owe me an explanation

377
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,090
for Lam's death.

378
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:24,010
Before the court session starts,

379
00:18:24,220 --> 00:18:25,460
let's not discuss this issue, okay?

380
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:27,220
I'm just worried about Yat-wai.

381
00:18:27,660 --> 00:18:28,730
You are busy with work,

382
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:30,220
and your car was stolen.

383
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:33,010
Who dares to steal a judge's car?

384
00:18:35,980 --> 00:18:37,010
Yat-wai is okay.

385
00:18:37,030 --> 00:18:38,090
And the car is found.

386
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:40,420
I'm really in a hurry now.

387
00:18:40,900 --> 00:18:41,700
Shall we meet some other day?

388
00:19:02,550 --> 00:19:03,010
Madam.

389
00:19:04,540 --> 00:19:05,380
I get nothing from him.

390
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:07,250
He refused to say anything
no matter what.

391
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,420
He is from the old town.

392
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,530
He has a criminal record
of stealing a car.

393
00:19:11,030 --> 00:19:12,090
I suspect he's one
of Chi Cheung-wing's people.

394
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:15,010
I just can't figure it out.

395
00:19:15,820 --> 00:19:17,090
Among so many cars on the street,

396
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:19,050
but why did he only
steal Mr. Chun's?

397
00:19:20,540 --> 00:19:21,180
Keep asking.

398
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:23,250
His attorney is here.

399
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:24,810
She waited for hours.

400
00:19:25,220 --> 00:19:25,900
Should we let her keep waiting?

401
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:28,860
It is the suspect's right
to see an attorney.

402
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:29,730
Let him see her.

403
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:30,900
OK.

404
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:32,330
Madam.

405
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:33,660
Something's found on the spot.

406
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:36,900
The Identification Squad found
paint traces that do not belong to it

407
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:38,420
[Forensic Evidence Examination Report]
on the motorcycle caused the accident.

408
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:39,490
It is estimated that it was left

409
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:40,730
after a violent collision
between two cars.

410
00:19:42,860 --> 00:19:43,620
Can they identify

411
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:44,570
what kind of car it is

412
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,090
through the traces of paint?

413
00:19:46,600 --> 00:19:48,770
They can only tell it's either
an European car or a Japanese car.

414
00:19:49,380 --> 00:19:51,140
Judging from the pieces of headlights
found at the scene,

415
00:19:51,700 --> 00:19:53,770
they said it was likely
to be a Japanese car.

416
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,010
But it can only be confirmed

417
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:56,290
after they find the car

418
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:57,010
that hit the motorcycle

419
00:19:57,320 --> 00:19:58,220
and have a forensic test.

420
00:19:58,940 --> 00:20:00,010
You said it's a Japanese car,

421
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:01,980
and there are collision traces.

422
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:03,420
And pieces of headlights were found

423
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,860
at the scene?

424
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:05,730
Yes, madam.

425
00:20:10,800 --> 00:20:12,920
[Lost Vehicle Retrieval Receipt]

426
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:16,320
[Judge, Chun Yue]

427
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:25,140
The police came to my school.

428
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:26,940
I... I ran.

429
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:37,330
Hello.

430
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:38,330
Yes.

431
00:20:38,350 --> 00:20:39,620
I am a parent of a student.

432
00:20:40,310 --> 00:20:41,940
I saw the police on the campus.

433
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:42,900
I wonder what happened.

434
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:48,530
A report on theft?

435
00:20:49,310 --> 00:20:50,250
Okay, thank you.

436
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:55,420
Come in.

437
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:57,900
Mr. Chun.

438
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:58,940
Ms. Tong is here.

439
00:21:00,310 --> 00:21:01,330
Ms. Tong, what's the matter?

440
00:21:02,270 --> 00:21:02,770
Mr. Chun.

441
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:04,420
May I ask where your car is now?

442
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:10,200
[Hokong Maximum Security Prison]

443
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:10,940
The doctor said

444
00:21:11,740 --> 00:21:13,220
Gong is in a stable condition now.

445
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:15,530
But still, it's serious.

446
00:21:17,220 --> 00:21:18,220
What matters the most

447
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:20,940
is whether he can wake up.

448
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:25,090
My son won't die so easily.

449
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:26,900
He will definitely get better.

450
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:31,290
Father.

451
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:33,770
I don't think Gong's case

452
00:21:34,300 --> 00:21:35,460
is an accident.

453
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,570
Just take good care of him now.

454
00:21:40,590 --> 00:21:42,180
Don't worry about anything else.

455
00:21:43,550 --> 00:21:46,090
The most important thing
is not to act rashly.

456
00:21:47,070 --> 00:21:48,460
It must be Chi Cheung-wing
and his men who did it!

457
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,810
That's why Gong was left by the road

458
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:51,700
like a waste.

459
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:53,980
No one dares to do so except them.

460
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,860
Just do what you love.

461
00:21:58,750 --> 00:22:00,180
Gong will take my position

462
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:01,860
in the future.

463
00:22:02,790 --> 00:22:04,250
You don't understand many things.

464
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:06,860
After he wakes up,

465
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:09,380
he'll naturally know what to do.

466
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:13,900
Father.

467
00:22:15,760 --> 00:22:17,090
I'm not trying to meddle with it.

468
00:22:18,900 --> 00:22:20,180
I just wanted to tell you

469
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:22,530
that he is not just your son,

470
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:24,980
but also my elder brother.

471
00:22:32,580 --> 00:22:33,330
I checked the scene.

472
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:36,730
It may have been left
by the person who hit him.

473
00:22:41,380 --> 00:22:41,720
OK.

474
00:22:43,180 --> 00:22:44,010
Hand it over to Ms. Lum.

475
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:45,940
She knows what to do.

476
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,420
Hand it over to the police.

477
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:50,180
Let them do what they should do.

478
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:51,810
I don't believe in them.

479
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,460
Do as I said!

480
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:03,730
Do you know why

481
00:23:04,340 --> 00:23:05,940
I try not to get you involved?

482
00:23:07,310 --> 00:23:09,140
Just in case.

483
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:12,220
I have two sons.

484
00:23:13,460 --> 00:23:15,010
I need to keep a way out for myself.

485
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,140
Do you really think

486
00:23:17,270 --> 00:23:18,530
the judge surnamed Chun

487
00:23:18,830 --> 00:23:20,050
is capable of convicting me

488
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,420
and sentencing me to jail?

489
00:23:22,580 --> 00:23:23,860
Matters in Hokong

490
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,660
are not as simple as you think.

491
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:38,460
The headlights have been replaced,

492
00:23:39,300 --> 00:23:40,380
but the scratches haven't been repaired.

493
00:23:42,420 --> 00:23:42,900
Yes.

494
00:23:43,940 --> 00:23:45,180
Because these scratches

495
00:23:45,380 --> 00:23:47,810
need to be repaired gradually
in the car repair shop.

496
00:23:48,340 --> 00:23:49,140
Since

497
00:23:49,180 --> 00:23:50,090
it didn't affect my driving,

498
00:23:50,140 --> 00:23:51,900
I planned to send it there
during my vacation.

499
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:54,290
Where was it repaired?

500
00:23:54,820 --> 00:23:56,580
I don't know which one it was,

501
00:23:56,580 --> 00:23:57,220
because

502
00:23:57,220 --> 00:23:58,660
the driver of the court
arranged it for me.

503
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:06,140
Hello?

504
00:24:07,100 --> 00:24:08,620
Now, go to the car repair shop
designated by the court.

505
00:24:09,040 --> 00:24:10,570
A champagne-gold Accord

506
00:24:10,900 --> 00:24:12,460
just had its headlight replaced there.

507
00:24:13,120 --> 00:24:14,660
Bring all parts and pieces

508
00:24:14,700 --> 00:24:15,660
back to me.

509
00:24:16,980 --> 00:24:17,420
OK.

510
00:24:21,140 --> 00:24:22,290
Is there something

511
00:24:22,340 --> 00:24:23,380
I need to know?

512
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:25,570
Mr. Chun.

513
00:24:26,340 --> 00:24:27,140
Now we suspect

514
00:24:27,840 --> 00:24:29,180
that the car which hit Hon Gong

515
00:24:29,820 --> 00:24:30,980
is the one you reported missing.

516
00:24:33,700 --> 00:24:34,570
Did the suspect plead guilty?

517
00:24:34,940 --> 00:24:35,140
No.

518
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:36,460
He didn't say anything,

519
00:24:36,900 --> 00:24:38,380
but we have enough evidence

520
00:24:38,620 --> 00:24:39,730
which shows it is very possible.

521
00:24:40,620 --> 00:24:41,530
So now,

522
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:42,540
I'll impound your car

523
00:24:42,540 --> 00:24:43,770
and let the Identification Bureau
deal with it.

524
00:24:44,380 --> 00:24:46,010
They'll collect evidence,
analysis and verify it,

525
00:24:46,520 --> 00:24:46,940
including

526
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:48,220
the scratches on the surface,

527
00:24:48,380 --> 00:24:49,330
the pieces of the headlights

528
00:24:49,620 --> 00:24:50,490
and these paints.

529
00:24:51,020 --> 00:24:51,570
Please

530
00:24:52,020 --> 00:24:52,900
sign here

531
00:24:53,060 --> 00:24:54,010
and give me the key.

532
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:55,810
When the Identification Bureau
finished it,

533
00:24:56,100 --> 00:24:56,770
you'll be notified.

534
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,040
How long will it take?

535
00:25:00,560 --> 00:25:01,090
Don't worry.

536
00:25:01,300 --> 00:25:02,380
I'll ask them

537
00:25:02,420 --> 00:25:03,290
to finish it as soon as possible.

538
00:25:04,380 --> 00:25:05,090
Mr. Chun.

539
00:25:05,940 --> 00:25:06,700
Ms. Tong.

540
00:25:07,340 --> 00:25:08,330
You work in joint hands again.

541
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:10,260
Which fool

542
00:25:10,260 --> 00:25:11,060
is so unlucky this time?

543
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:18,140
Mr. Chun is the light of justice
in our court.

544
00:25:18,840 --> 00:25:20,330
With the support
of the police force now,

545
00:25:20,980 --> 00:25:22,490
he has a really high popularity.

546
00:25:23,160 --> 00:25:24,330
Running for president of the court,

547
00:25:24,740 --> 00:25:25,570
your reputation

548
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:26,620
is indeed impressive!

549
00:25:28,020 --> 00:25:29,050
Mr. Lo, you flattered me.

550
00:25:31,820 --> 00:25:32,810
I'll let you guys continue.

551
00:25:33,500 --> 00:25:34,620
A strong cooperation.

552
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:40,660
Mr. Chun.

553
00:25:41,580 --> 00:25:43,140
I'd like to ask you for a favor.

554
00:25:55,580 --> 00:25:57,220
You can tell me who hit you.

555
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:58,460
I can accuse him.

556
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:05,770
Are they intimidating you

557
00:26:05,840 --> 00:26:06,700
and trying to falsely accuse you?

558
00:26:08,080 --> 00:26:09,330
If you don't say it, next time,

559
00:26:09,350 --> 00:26:10,620
they might treat you worse.

560
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:12,940
As long as you stand up bravely,

561
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:15,460
I can sue them for excessive violence.

562
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:16,380
No need.

563
00:26:18,060 --> 00:26:18,300
I

564
00:26:18,780 --> 00:26:19,700
don't want to get into more trouble.

565
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:25,770
You have more trouble?

566
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:33,960
Are you now asking me

567
00:26:34,060 --> 00:26:34,900
